Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.TUI.components.printables

Class CardBack

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.view.TUI.components.printables.CardBack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<String>
public abstract class CardBack extends Object implements Iterable<String>
Abstract class representing different card backs in a board game. Provides ASCII art representations for different resource types. Implements Iterable for easy iteration over its contents.
